§§ Notation ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ We denote the epigraph of a function $f$ by $\epi f$. ⦉
⦉

§ Extension to extended real numbers ⦉
¶ ⦊
  ‖ We can extend this concept in the natural way to extended
    real value function $f: D → \Rbar$.
    ◇ ⦊
      ‖ \epi f \Set{(x, α) ∈ D × 𝗥}{f(x) ≤ α} ⦉
    ⦉⦉

  ‖ Caution, in this case $f \not⊂ \epi f$. ⦉
⦉

